{"type": "article", "id": 31805, "title": "Herschel Supply 收购 Totokaelo，以及，推荐一组牛仔背包 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-05T02:42:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10357, "name": "日本市场"}, {"id": 32381, "name": "鲨鱼迷彩"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 7260, "name": "Club Monaco"}, {"id": 8086, "name": "Saucony"}, {"id": 17867, "name": "Herschel Supply"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 32382, "name": "Eastpak"}, {"id": 32383, "name": "banila.co"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016090509072994ELndMJSWrvI2mt.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/asos-com-to-pay-26-2m-to-settle-trademark-infringement-disputes-10520130/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>时尚电商 ASOS 斥资 2020 万英镑解决商标纠纷</b></a> | ASOS 解决了与瑞士 cyclewear 制造商 Assos 以及德国男装零售商 Anson’s Herrenhaus 在商标版权上的纠纷。ASOS 仍限制在德国 Anson’s Herrenhaus 开实体店，而瑞士 Assos 已经行使授予的权利，并将在伦敦开一家店。 该诉讼案的胜利，意味着 ASOS 将被允许进入运动休闲市场。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/a-guide-to-fashion-immediacy\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 旗下品牌 Club Monaco 将首次亮相纽约时装周</b></a> | 9 月 9 日，Club Monaco 将登陆纽约时装周。本次，它将展出男装女装线的 37 个造型，并且实行与时装周同步，“即看即买”的策略。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/department-stores/japan-retailers-see-lower-sales-in-august-10519981/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>日本零售市场八月表现不佳</b></a> | 受台风天气以及节假日过少等因素影响，日本的零售市场八月业绩低迷。其中，优衣库的母公司迅销集团在日本市场的销售同比下滑了 1%。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/totokaelo-herschel-supply-co-jill-wenger\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>加拿大箱包品牌 Herschel Supply 收购 Totokaelo</b></a> | 诞生于西雅图的年轻时尚零售商 Totokaelo，去年秋天在纽约中心区 SOHO 开设了一家约 780 平方米的店铺。该公司现被加拿大箱包品牌 Herschel Supply 收购。收购后，Totokaelo 首席执行官 Wenger 的职位仍保持不变。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/retailing/the-body-shop-opens-chile-10520438/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国护肤品牌 The Body Shop 进军智利市场</b></a> | The Body Shop 在智利开了一家 65 平方米的店铺，作为它进军智利市场的开端。智利是 The Body Shop 在南美的第二个国家市场，2014 年，The Body Shop 在巴西开设首家店铺，现在，它在巴西的店铺已经扩张到了 100 家。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/saucony-grid-9000-pastel\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saucony Grid 9000 发布两款全新配色</a>，该系列鞋身采用皮革、网眼与氯丁橡胶结合制作，有粉红和淡绿两种配色。定价为 120 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093321a8v3qI4R5UYcH0PG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093330TFbxBy9rhYED8f70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609050933391tu0qEgYTZBnLGWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Eastpak 推出全新<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/eastpak-boro-kuroki-denim-backpacks\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Padded Pak’rs 高品质单宁背包系列</a>。该系列以经典背包为原型，通过缝补拼接手法来致敬日本传统的 Boro 制作工艺。</p><p class=\"\">这五款背包的定价均为 1120 美元。</p><p class=\"\">此外，Eastpak 还与日本冈山的 Kuroki 合作，推出了两款轻微水洗的丹宁背包。这两款背包的定价为 145 美元。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093259CQPo21DtxKShgAyZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093311tw5KqO390EpU4TMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>纽约时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/aime-leon-dore-latest-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aimé Leon Dore 发布 2016 秋冬新品系列</a>。该系列延续了品牌一往的简约都市风格。有连帽夹克、长短袖 tee、水洗牛仔裤、印花围巾以及白色托特包等。售价为 45 到 375 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090509322616DpNST0uIiBPRrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609050932388GVqAjPBCH54gdbM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093249tD9GRkiqBePXZQKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/banila-co-iphoria-collection/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">banila.co 与德国品牌 IPHORIA 合作推出秋冬限定彩妆系列</a>，包括气垫粉底、唇彩和眼影盘。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093207YcehPldJDo9Zq51X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093207lbVDouwFMNBXd9Sz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609050932075T3nUmhoXZOgLVcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093213c0GBr4lX2LiUPSf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093213hcvuT8Mk9CtfIaZG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/bape-shark-items-fall-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 推出了 2016 年全新鲨鱼迷彩系列</a>。该系列的亮点单品 A Bathing Ape Color Camo Mil Wide Pullover Jacket ，售价为 33800 日元。官方网站和 BAPE 门店现已全部发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093011ZEKoinlbw1A9tYhG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093011BA7w429g6xLsuWNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093012CKG8wVJpYFM6ax7g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093011G4MefuldCaZLswt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093022zHcujefT7B0nVdaQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093022ZWOgwjsK7TQ02znS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609050930227dP6EruDi21xBjHq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093156bQlE7KgosFTxpyfA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905093157vAETe0oRJc3y9tPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}